4. Play Menu:
Picture 3.4 Picture 4.4
In Picture (3.4) Normal Play menu buton when hover the
buton with Mouse cursor Picture (4.4) and if click on it play
menu shows up in Picture (5.4).
Picture 5.4
In play menu there are three blocks. Nick Box, Start Button and Menu
Button. If player wants to enter your nick in the Nick Box, he/she click on it and
enter her/his nick.After entering click Enter Key to finish nick enter
process.Also nick lenght between 4 and 8 characters.
After enter an acceptable nick, you can hit start buton and start playing
the game. But you want to turn back to the main menu hit the home buton.
5. Options Menu:
Picture 6.5
See Options Menu in Picture (6.5). This menu includes game playground
settings.
1. Screen Size:
There are three choices 460x280, 720x460(default setting) and 1080x720. You can
change it click left and right arrows.
2. FPS(Game Play Speed):
Also there are three choices in here; slow, medium and fast.
3. Fruit (Snake Foods):
There are six choices in here as default setting is peach.
4. Background Color:
Three choices in here also: green, light orange and yellow; because of that the snake
has color and the enemy has color so there are no more color options.
5. Sound:
You can mute/unmute the game and menu sounds in here.
6. How to Play Menu:
In this menu includes how to play this game manual. You
can read and learn how to play it.
7. High Score Menu:
Picture 7.7
In this menu includes high score have ever done. First, second and third
person include. Also you can go main menu with home buton.
8. Quit Button:
When hit on it, the game screen will be close.
